title: Eagle Peak (San Bernardino County, California)
text:
Eagle Peak is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> <a href="Peak%20%28topography%29">peak</a> located in <a href="San%20Bernardino%20County%2C%20California">San Bernardino County</a>, <a href="California">California</a>.
The <a href="Summit%20%28topography%29">summit</a> is in elevation making it the highest mountain in the <a href="Sacramento%20Mountains%20%28California%29">Sacramento Mountains</a>.
